title: #338 SAMANTHA BEE IS FINISHED! Gavin McInnes and Tommy Robinson* Guest
description: Talking all things Samantha Bee and her now infamous remarks regarding Ivanka Trump, Kim Kardashian’s trip to the White House, UK knife control, OBGYN fails and more. Gavin McInnes stops by to talk the state of comedy and censorship, and *Tommy Robinson’s manager, Caolan Robertson, stops in to give us an update on Tommy following his recent imprisonment!
